<div class="forum-post-quote"><p class="forum-post-quoted-name">Directcontact</p><p style="margin-top:0;">And it doesn't seem to need me to "believe" in it -- b/c it seems to believe in me.</p><p>With love,</p><p>Dawn</p></div><p>Beautiful way to say it!  I have the same feeling but never thought of it that way. Life believes in me.   Lera</p>
</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-post" -->
